<p>If you are looking for that perfect destination vacation to cure the winter blues, then slap leather, and head to Wickenburg Arizona. Believe me, the quality of the riding here rules! With an incredibly large area, there is pristine desert singletrack for every skill level. You can ride for a week solid and not see it all. Daytime temps average 60 to 70 most of the winter months, this is an incredible experience on a motorcycle. OMR operates from Wickenburg November 1 through March, don&#8217;t miss this! Great lodging can be had at Rancho-Casitas guest ranch, a retro- 60&#8217;s dude ranch, find them online for more info. <img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2577" src="https://www.oregonmotorcyclerental.com/newsite/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Arizona-Motorcycle-Training-300x214.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="214" srcset="../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Arizona-Motorcycle-Training-300x214.jpg 300w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Arizona-Motorcycle-Training-768x548.jpg 768w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Arizona-Motorcycle-Training-205x146.jpg 205w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Arizona-Motorcycle-Training-50x36.jpg 50w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Arizona-Motorcycle-Training-105x75.jpg 105w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Arizona-Motorcycle-Training.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width:767px) 300px, 300px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2590" src="https://www.oregonmotorcyclerental.com/newsite/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Singletrack-Motorcycle-Clinic-7-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" srcset="../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Singletrack-Motorcycle-Clinic-7-300x200.jpg 300w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Singletrack-Motorcycle-Clinic-7-768x512.jpg 768w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Singletrack-Motorcycle-Clinic-7-219x146.jpg 219w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Singletrack-Motorcycle-Clinic-7-50x33.jpg 50w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Singletrack-Motorcycle-C